# Standards Design System

## Color Palette

### Primary Colors (Blue)
- `primary-500`: Main actions, CTAs, links (#558BF4)
- Use `bg-primary-500`, `text-primary-500`, `border-primary-500`

### Secondary Colors (Dark Blue)
- `secondary-500`: Navigation, headers (#003155)
- Use for dark backgrounds and secondary actions

### Semantic Colors
- `destructive`: Error states, delete actions (#E7000B)
- `success`: Success states, confirmations (#08826F)
- `warning`: Warning states, cautions (#E77700)
- `info`: Information, tips (#155DFC)

### Neutral Colors (Legacy from template)
- `n-1` to `n-8`: Grayscale from white to dark
- `n-8`: Main dark background
- `n-1`: Main light text

## Typography

### Font Family
- **Manrope** is the primary font
- Available weights: 200-800
- Use `font-sans` class (configured in globals.css)

### Heading Classes
- `.h1`: Hero headings (responsive: 2.5rem → 3.75rem)
- `.h2`: Section headings (responsive: 1.75rem → 3rem)
- `.h3`: Subsection headings
- `.h4`, `.h5`, `.h6`: Smaller headings

### Body Classes
- `.body-1`: Large body text (responsive)
- `.body-2`: Regular body text
- `.caption`: Small text
- `.tagline`: Uppercase tracking labels

## Spacing
- Use Tailwind spacing utilities
- Custom: `px-15` (3.75rem), `px-7.5` (1.875rem)

## Dark Mode
- Dark mode is enabled via `next-themes`
- Uses `class` strategy on `<html>`
- CSS variables automatically switch in `.dark` class

## Animations
- Default transition: 200ms linear
- Use `transition-colors` for hover states
- Accordion animations available via `animate-accordion-down/up`
